        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Bangkok/_scene_tiger.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository ead42816-44a3-40b2-ae9d-675a140a6671).Image",
        "Description": "Max B. and Jed Pitt are friends who share the same birthday as Jordan Cross. To celebrate, they plan on heading down to the bar after work with a local to help navigate them through Bangkok’s markets. They are apart of the planning committee for the rockstar’s day so that they can get out of their faster. Knuckles even wants to punch some lights out to ensure that him, Max, and their guide make it before sunrise.\rOriginal contract by @Ashley on HMF",
